about.description: Fast, compiled object-oriented algorithms and enabling technologies for the solution of large-scale, complex multi-physics engineering and scientific problems.
about.summary: Sandia's suite of HPC solvers and enabling technologies

name: trilinos
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "Trilinos" %}
{% set version = "12.10.1" %}
{% set sha256 = "ea8ff573bb1f452f2585950cdabe7e2c84cb35013844c58dc878c66bd4245e06" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: trilinos-{{ version }}-Source.tar.gz
  url: http://trilinos.csbsju.edu/download/files/trilinos-{{ version }}-Source.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  skip: true  # [win or py3k]

requirements:
  build:
    - cmake >=2.8.11
    - toolchain
    - openmpi
    - python
    - openblas 0.2.19|0.2.19.*

  run:
    - openmpi
    - openblas 0.2.19|0.2.19.*

test:
  commands:
    - test -f $PREFIX/include/TeuchosCore_ConfigDefs.hpp
    - test -f $PREFIX/lib/libteuchoscore.12.10.1.dylib    # [osx]
    - test -f $PREFIX/lib/libteuchoscore.so.12.10.1       # [linux]

about:
  home: https://trilinos.org
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary:
    Sandia's suite of HPC solvers and enabling technologies
  description:
    Fast, compiled object-oriented algorithms and enabling
    technologies for the solution of large-scale, complex
    multi-physics engineering and scientific problems.
  dev_url: https://github.com/trilinos/Trilinos

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - wfspotz

about.description: Fast, compiled object-oriented algorithms and enabling technologies for the solution of large-scale, complex multi-physics engineering and scientific problems.
about.summary: Sandia's suite of HPC solvers and enabling technologies
